# why not jekyll's auto md->html?

jekyll plugin is not allowed if you want to host your site on github server https://github.com/mojombo/jekyll/wiki/Plugins

jekyll's own gfm, has a quite limited feature set, that's why they are considering use multimarkdown
https://github.com/mojombo/jekyll/issues/289
